oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Andrew Jackson returns to Nashville
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Print depicting Andrew Jackson in a carriage drawn by a dark and a light horse. The carriage has a driver and a footman, as well as one other passenger. Troops and buildings in the background. Civilians in foreground. Return to Nashvillle
A depiction of Andrew Jackson's return to Nashville after the conclusion of the War of 1812.
